Model 1: Intercept-only Model

m1 <- glmer(
  data = df_RQ1, 
  formula = hgt ~ 1 + (1 | CHILD), 
  family = binomial(link = "logit"), 
  control = glmerControl(optimizer = "bobyqa", optCtrl = list(maxfun = 2000000))
)

saveRDS(m1, file = "models/m1_intercept_only_RQ1.rds")

Model 2: Fixed Effect of F1

m2_fixed_F1 <- glmer(
  data = df_RQ1, 
  formula = hgt ~ F1_Regression_Normalized + (1 | CHILD), 
  family = binomial(link = "logit"), 
  control = glmerControl(optimizer = "bobyqa", optCtrl = list(maxfun = 10000000))
)

saveRDS(m2_fixed_F1, file = "models/m2_F1_fixed_effect_RQ1.rds")
anova_results_m2 <- anova(m1, m2_fixed_F1)
print(anova_results_m2)

â¡ï¸ The added predictor F1_Regression_Normalized significantly improves the model fit and was retained for further analysis.

Model 3: Random Slope for F1

m3_random_slope_F1 <- glmer(
  data = df_RQ1, 
  formula = hgt ~ F1_Regression_Normalized + (1 + F1_Regression_Normalized | CHILD), 
  family = binomial(link = "logit"), 
  control = glmerControl(optimizer = "bobyqa", optCtrl = list(maxfun = 10000000))
)

saveRDS(m3_random_slope_F1, file = "models/m3_random_slope_F1_RQ1.rds")
anova_results_m3 <- anova(m2_fixed_F1, m3_random_slope_F1)
print(anova_results_m3)

â¡ï¸ The added random slope for F1_Regression_Normalized significantly improves the model fit and was retained for further analysis.

# Define color palettes
F1_color <- c("#8F3400", "#FF681F", "#FFBE8F")
F0_color <- c("#570887", "#A020F0", "#D387F8")

# Define a function for plotting
create_plot <- function(model, term1, term2, colors, y_label, x_label, legend_title) {
  plot <- plot_model(model, type = "pred", terms = c("AGE_ctrd [all]", term2, term1)
                     , pred.type = "fe",
                     mdrt.values = "meansd"
                     ) +
    labs(
      color = legend_title,
      y = y_label,
      x = x_label,
      title = ""
    ) +
    theme_cowplot() +
    scale_color_manual(values = colors) +
    scale_fill_manual(values = colors) +
    scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format(), limits = c(0, 1)) +
    theme(legend.position = "bottom", legend.box = "horizontal")
  return(plot)
}
